name: AEAssessmentSessionDelegate
desc: An interface that the session uses to provide information about session state changes to a delegate.

items.name: func assessmentSessionDidBegin(AEAssessmentSession)
items.desc: Tells the delegate that the session started.

items.name: func assessmentSession(AEAssessmentSession, failedToBeginWithError: Error)
items.desc: Tells the delegate that the session failed to start.

items.name: func assessmentSession(AEAssessmentSession, wasInterruptedWithError: Error)
items.desc: Tells the delegate that a system failure interrupted the session.

items.name: func assessmentSessionDidEnd(AEAssessmentSession)
items.desc: Tells the delegate that the session ended.

items.name: func assessmentSessionDidUpdate(AEAssessmentSession)
items.desc: Tells the delegate that a configuration update succeeded.

items.name: func assessmentSession(AEAssessmentSession, failedToUpdateTo: AEAssessmentConfiguration, error: Error)
items.desc: Tells the delegate that a configuration update failed.

items.name: struct AEAssessmentError
items.desc: Errors issued by an assessment session to its delegate.
